</div>=20

<p>For example, the <b>15th</b> Lucas Number is approximately =CF=86<sup>15=
</sup> <em>=3D</em> 1364,0007..., so is exactly <b>1364</b>. Try it yoursel=
f!</p>=20
</div>


<div class=3D"fun">=20

<h3>Here is the Fibonacci sequence again:</h3>=20

<div class=3D"beach">

