<div class=3D"fun">=20

<h3>Fibonacci Words</h3>=20

<div style=3D"margin-left: 20px;"> I<br>
have<br>
a poem<br>
about a sequence<br>
that will not stop growin'<br>
where each line has as many words as<br>
the previous two lines combined which sounds real easy but can so rapidly<b=
r>
